        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-4d1c93f2-b3d3-48d5-acf6-fb8eedd507bd">
                Mr. George Chetwynd
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-4d1c93f2-b3d3-48d5-acf6-fb8eedd507bd" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-02-21/debates/1cce6e4e-0bea-4957-ba3d-f7c2e042a344/Ministers(AcceptanceOfGifts)#contribution-4d1c93f2-b3d3-48d5-acf6-fb8eedd507bd">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Prime Minister what conditions govern the acceptance by Ministers of the Crown, in pursuance of their duties, of gifts and services from commercial undertakings.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-4d1c93f2-b3d3-48d5-acf6-fb8eedd507bd" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
